thread.section_title: Wiggle Reviews | Customer Service Reviews of Wiggle | wiggle.com.au
thread.title: Mo

author: Mo
title: Mo
text:
Good range of products
Good pricing on most products
Good service
Good online chat service also
BUT
Delivery time is very very ordinary
3 weeks from date of picking and packing is a turn off
Absolutely no reason to have a online shop with .com.au when all items are dispatched from the U.K.
This too is misleading
Dissapointing because today's freight services are price and time competitive so there should be no issues
